r 11h trading window.\n\n**If TREND persists at 11h:** Bot stays stopped. Correct behavior \u2014 our 73% WR is RANGE-only.\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-30 02:42 UTC \u2014 Pillar 2: Regime Detector Hysteresis Fix\n\n**Task:** Fix watchdog/regime detector restart loop.\n\n**Problem:** Regime oscillates between TREND and MIXED at boundaries. Each MIXED reading removed STOP flag \u2192 watchdog restarted bot \u2192 next TREND reading stopped it again. Cycle every 30 min.\n\n**Fix:** Added 2-reading hysteresis to regime detector:\n1. First non-TREND reading after TREND \u2192 enters cooldown (flag stays)\n2. Second consecutive non-TREND \u2192 removes flag (bot restarts)\n3. Any TREND reading resets cooldown counter\n\n**Effect:** Bot now needs 30 min (2 \u00d7 15-min checks) of sustained non-TREND before restarting. Eliminates churn at regime boundaries. When regime genuinely returns to RANGE, bot still starts within 30 min.\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-30 02:08 UTC \u2014 ALERT: STOP_TRADING Flag Active (Regime=TREND)\n\n**Discovery:** pm-bot screen missing! Regime detector set STOP_TRADING at 01:00 UTC (TREND score 5/8).\n\n**Root cause:** BTC recovered from $64,904 to $66,771 (+",
